4 16:45:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-251-who-says-1-600-kids-in-gaza-under-5-treated-for-acute-malnutrition/00000190-1277-d529-adb2-3777f1e40000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡欺骗美国 现在拜登需要就如何结束加沙战争做出艰难决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-conned-the-u-s-now-biden-must-make-tough-decisions-on-how-to-end-the-gaza-war/00000190-11e7-df06-adb8-71e717240000</link><description>经过八个月的推行最终失败的政策后，美国总统乔·拜登可以采取哪些现实且可执行的政策选择来解决冲突？本质上，有两种非常困难的选择——另一种同样令人不安但可行</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 16:28:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-conned-the-u-s-now-biden-must-make-tough-decisions-on-how-to-end-the-gaza-war/00000190-11e7-df06-adb8-71e717240000</guid></item><item><title>40 枚火箭、5 架无人机、十几起火灾：真主党连续第二天袭击以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/40-rockets-5-drones-a-dozen-fires-hezbollah-pounds-israels-north-for-second-day/00000190-11d1-d529-adb2-37d59cbf0000</link><description>真主党周四向以色列戈兰高地和加利利发射火箭弹、导弹和攻击无人机后，该组织内部消息人士称，这是自加沙战争爆发以来最大规模的袭击</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 15:38:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/40-rockets-5-drones-a-dozen-fires-hezbollah-pounds-israels-north-for-second-day/00000190-11d1-d529-adb2-37d59cbf0000</guid></item><item><title>来自黎巴嫩南部的声音：“我们不支持以色列，但反对真主党的运作方式”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/voices-from-southern-lebanon-we-dont-support-israel-but-oppose-how-hezbollah-operates/00000190-1171-d667-abf0-75fbe3e60000</link><description>黎巴嫩南部居民议论：拉米的生活在真主党对以色列展开战线的那一天就停止了，纳贾特在生下双胞胎后立即逃离，尼扎尔的村庄正在巡逻，以将真主党拒之门外。在南方，悲观情绪盛行</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 14:55:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/voices-from-southern-lebanon-we-dont-support-israel-but-oppose-how-hezbollah-operates/00000190-1171-d667-abf0-75fbe3e60000</guid></item><item><title>受热浪影响，东耶路撒冷巴勒斯坦社区供水减少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/water-supply-reduced-in-palestinian-neighborhood-in-east-jerusalem-amid-heat-wave/00000190-1170-d667-abf0-75fbf3850000</link><description>尽管位于市政线内，卡法阿卡布社区还是从一家巴勒斯坦公司获得水，该公司表示，以色列向其输送的水量减少了。据当地人称，该社区本周只停了两天水。以色列自来水公司：这是巴勒斯坦权力机构的责任</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 13:31:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/water-supply-reduced-in-palestinian-neighborhood-in-east-jerusalem-amid-heat-wave/00000190-1170-d667-abf0-75fbf3850000</guid></item><item><title>离开哈佛后的生活：韦克斯纳基金会的以色列领导人计划有何前景？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/life-after-harvard-where-is-wexner-foundations-israeli-leaders-program-heading/00000190-113e-db28-a995-55bf25940000</link><description>总部位于美国的韦克斯纳基金会多年来一直在运行其享有盛誉的哈佛大学奖学金项目，但在哈佛大学对针对以色列的抗议活动做出反应后，中止了与哈佛大学的合作关系。以色列同胞讲述他们度过的艰难的一年</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 13:16:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/life-after-harvard-where-is-wexner-foundations-israeli-leaders-program-heading/00000190-113e-db28-a995-55bf25940000</guid></item><item><title>英国工党领袖在下个月预期的胜利之前承诺建立巴勒斯坦国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/uk-labour-leader-commits-to-palestinian-state-ahead-of-next-months-anticipated-victory/00000190-1153-d9aa-afd9-1f7f233e0000</link><description>工党领袖基尔·斯塔默(Keir Starmer)在党内批评他在以色列-哈马斯战争问题上的立场后，发表了党内选举宣言，称承认巴勒斯坦必须成为“新和平进程”的一部分</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 12:22:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/uk-labour-leader-commits-to-palestinian-state-ahead-of-next-months-anticipated-victory/0