gazine/.premium/the-terrorists-killed-mom-and-her-boyfriend-i-ducked-and-i-ran/00000190-021a-dbe3-a1da-133f25fa0000</link><description>“恐怖分子杀死了妈妈和她的男朋友。我躲开并逃跑”：来自乌克兰的男孩静静地躺着，等待哈马斯的恐怖分子离开。体内中弹的他躲在斯德洛特一个陌生人的家里，直到第二天，一个陌生人主动提出帮助他</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 09:19:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-terrorists-killed-mom-and-her-boyfriend-i-ducked-and-i-ran/00000190-021a-dbe3-a1da-133f25fa0000</guid></item><item><title>美国在沙特阿拉伯的利益正受到以色列极右翼救世主部长的破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/american-interests-in-saudi-arabia-are-being-torpedoed-by-israels-far-right-ministers/00000190-064e-d067-adb0-8e6e1a840000</link><description>沙特与美国的防务协议将服务于以色列的安全理论和美国的战略，但它与内塔尼亚胡在政治上所信奉的救世主观点相冲突，使得以色列成为伊朗的合作伙伴，共同阻挠该协议</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 07:41:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/american-interests-in-saudi-arabia-are-being-torpedoed-by-israels-far-right-ministers/00000190-064e-d067-adb0-8e6e1a840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列官员：尽管哈马斯“有效拒绝”拜登计划，加沙谈判仍在继续</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sources-despite-hamas-effective-rejection-of-biden-plan-hostage-talks-to-go-on/00000190-0e02-dfa9-a9fc-cfd7b04a0000</link><description>尽管哈马斯要求对以美框架进行重大改变，但以色列和外国消息人士表示，卡塔尔和埃及将继续与美国协调，看看能否达成协议</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 03:03:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-sources-despite-hamas-effective-rejection-of-biden-plan-hostage-talks-to-go-on/00000190-0e02-dfa9-a9fc-cfd7b04a0000</guid></item><item><title>官员表示，美国“非常关注”以色列和黎巴嫩之间的“重大升级”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article-live/hamas-urges-u-s-to-pressure-israel-in-effort-to-reach-ceasefire/00000190-0f3d-db28-a995-4fbd6d670000</link><description>以色列北部大规模火箭弹袭击造成两人受伤 ■ 以色列政府发言人表示，黎巴嫩、真主党和伊朗对边境冲突负有全部责任 ■ 真主党消息人士向半岛电视台透露：对以色列的最新攻击是自 10 月 8 日以来最大规模的袭击 ■ 以色列军队表示地面安全部队、战斗机瞄准拉法的哈马斯 ■ 哈马斯敦促美国向以色列施压以达成协议，称其对停火计划的拟议修正案“并不重要”</description><pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 01:55:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-13/ty-article-live/hamas-urges-u-s-to-pressure-israel-in-effort-to-reach-ceasefire/00000190-0f3d-db28-a995-4fbd6d670000</guid></item><item><title>与伊朗挂钩，北方火箭弹袭击背后：被以色列杀害的真主党将军是谁？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/tied-to-iran-behind-rocket-fire-on-north-who-was-the-hezbollah-general-killed-by-israel/00000190-0d68-db28-a995-4dfdbd230000</link><description>以色列军方表示，真主党高级指挥官塔勒布·萨米·阿卜杜拉是自 10 月敌对行动开始以来被杀的最高级别官员；以色列国防军还提到，他对真主党拥有重要的行动知识</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 18:43:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/tied-to-iran-behind-rocket-fire-on-north-who-was-the-hezbollah-general-killed-by-israel/00000190-0d68-db28-a995-4dfdbd230000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列和哈马斯不达成协议，加沙战斗将漫无目的地拖延，北部可能陷入全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/without-israel-hamas-deal-gaza-fighting-will-drag-on-as-north-may-plunge-into-all-out-war/00000190-0d69-d0f9-a1d5-dd6940190000</link><description>辛瓦尔的结束战争要求是内塔尼亚胡无意满足的，这让拜登政府不知所措 ■ 以色列在没有明确战略的情况下加大对真主党高级领导人的打击力度，纳斯鲁拉则升级报复性袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:46:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/.premium/without-israel-hamas-deal-gaza-fighting-will-drag-on-as-north-may-plunge-into-all-out-war/00000190-0d69-d0f9-a1d5-dd6940190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，边境敌对行动达到顶峰时，真主党向以色列北部发射了 200 多枚火箭弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/idf-says-hezbollah-fired-over-200-rockets-at-israels-north-as-border-hostilities-peak/00000190-0ca4-dfa9-a9fc-cff52fe00000</link><description>这次大规模袭击是在真主党在冲突中伤亡最高的人员被杀之后发生的。以色列国防军官员表示，以色列尚未决定对黎巴嫩进行大规模军事反应</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/idf-says-hezbollah-fired-over-200-rockets-at-israels-north-as-border-hostilities-peak/00000190-0ca4-dfa9-a9fc-cff52fe00000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯要求以色列在休战一周内从加沙撤军，并首先释放人质尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/hamas-responds-to-egypt-qatar-on-gaza-cease-fire-and-hostage-release-plan/00000190-08db-d0f9-a1d5-d8fb2b450000</link><description>哈马斯消息人士告诉《国土报》，此举“旨在确保以色列无法逃避协议的所有阶段，并在所有人质获释后重新投入战斗。”以色列称哈马斯的回应等于拒绝该提议本身</description><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 17:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-12/ty-article/hamas-responds-to-egypt-qatar-on-gaza-cease-fire-and-hostage-release-plan/00000190-08db-d0f9-a1d5-d8fb2b450000</guid></item></channel></rss>